Package org.conqat.lib.simulink.model.datahandler

This package contains code for interpreting the model's data in a version independent way and add a more abstract layer on some of the information (including layout information).

Package org.conqat.lib.simulink.model.datahandler Description

This package contains code for interpreting the model's data in a version independent way and add a more abstract layer on some of the information (including layout information). For this we implement a data handler that has version specific subclasses.
